Class RpnEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • RpnEvaluator

  • public class RpnEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to evaluate reverse polish notation expressions. This class only outputs an answer when an expression is valid.
    Author:
    Jake Ira, Nick Sosinski
